  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >The game will surely appeal to those who still remember or love the good old 8-bit games from the 80s</h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3110310/extras/76f5cdddc27a070dda7db9dcc8e1669b.avif?t=1726732378\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3110310/extras_big/76f5cdddc27a070dda7db9dcc8e1669b.avif?t=1726732378 width=800 height=548 /></span><br><br>A leisurely and exciting passage of 56 levels with endless attempts will allow you to relax and have fun.<br><br>Collect all the bolts so that your flying saucer can launch and send you to the next level.<br><br>Move items carefully to avoid getting blocked. Otherwise you will have to start the level from the beginning.<br><br>Find batteries to charge your weapon and get rid of obstacles or enemies on your way.<br>Try to choose a direct collision with alien creatures, it is deadly =(<br><br>Use portals to access closed places and keys to open doors.",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >The game will surely appeal to those who still remember or love the good old 8-bit games from the 80s</h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3110310/extras/76f5cdddc27a070dda7db9dcc8e1669b.avif?t=1726732378\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3110310/extras_big/76f5cdddc27a070dda7db9dcc8e1669b.avif?t=1726732378 width=800 height=548 /></span><br><br>A leisurely and exciting passage of 56 levels with endless attempts will allow you to relax and have fun.<br><br>Collect all the bolts so that your flying saucer can launch and send you to the next level.<br><br>Move items carefully to avoid getting blocked. Otherwise you will have to start the level from the beginning.<br><br>Find batteries to charge your weapon and get rid of obstacles or enemies on your way.<br>Try to choose a direct collision with alien creatures, it is deadly =(<br><br>Use portals to access closed places and keys to open doors.",
